{"tid":874680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港史上最靚煙花】青馬大橋開幕    戴卓爾夫人主持儀式","createTime":"2018-10-24T11:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T13:54:17.000Z","uid":60281,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"64c8efc4a93637ca06512f64cf26adac9c636413","tid":874680,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"個瀑布靚到而家都好記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20070427/large/27la9p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070427%2Flarge%2F27la9p1.jpg&h=62c95219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rXOWQ5o24A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrXOWQ5o24A4&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=978c807d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rXOWQ5o24A4</a><br />\n<br />\n作為港英政府玫瑰園計劃的其中一個項目，青馬大橋在97年4月27日開幕，當時更由英國前首相戴卓爾夫人親臨香港主持儀式。當晚，有10萬人在璀璨的煙花滙演下，見證這個歷史時刻，卻除了一個人，就是時為候任特首的董建華。<br />\n董建華當日以到廣州公幹為由，沒出席大橋開幕禮。不過，有人揣測他刻意避開，不想與末代港督彭定康和戴卓爾夫人等同場，而當時中方駐港主要官員都缺席，包括獲邀的新華社前社長周南。大橋5月22日正式通車，主跨長1,377米，連引道全長為2,160米。十年來，青馬大橋已是本港重要樞紐。<br />\n<br />\n好狀觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eH0vEyb2cHI?t=196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeH0vEyb2cHI%3Ft%3D196&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=53f2d5b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eH0vEyb2cHI?t=196</a>"},{"pid":"e4caa053cbdc32a1193d31c016b4a49b08ea0efc","tid":874680,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913466b7275304f58f17cae2b0f4685b01890552","tid":874680,"uid":155344,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"呢d就真係長線發展啦"},{"pid":"c76fcfed41b9c1c8da74edcdad53c02e7f774c45","tid":874680,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"當年係現場睇<br />\n真係好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e3654fd43ff7f82c4a3c20ff6905e99a9d08fb","tid":874680,"uid":18245,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n越睇越傷心"},{"pid":"9d0192e1fd99a6e229de50be5054880432af9898","tid":874680,"uid":61018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"一諗起港豬果個電子煙花真係笑撚死"},{"pid":"92b7b270f6e8d2a36b730b5418155f1a5181c72f","tid":874680,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:59:41.000Z","msg":"想當年都仲有亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3de118833c51187140a81108b94d7e2e10bf880","tid":874680,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:59:45.000Z","msg":"青馬大橋=香港命脈"},{"pid":"26068c86e1c36d8183d30f12f7d0322c85095668","tid":874680,"uid":100276,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/200159_72943f153762035d963cfa0573479f52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F200159_72943f153762035d963cfa0573479f52.png&h=58719622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14723100608f5b708b034477532